Class DependenciesExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.plan.DependenciesExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionVisitor

    public class DependenciesExtractor
extends Object
implements ActionVisitor
    Detect dependencies between actions. Actions are inserted using #visit(...) methods.
